HEADWORD: span-new
<hw>span"-new`</hw> <pr>(sp⟦acr⟧n"n⟦umac⟧`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Icel. <ets>sp⟦amac⟧nn⟦ymac⟧r</ets>, properly, new as a ship just
split; <ets>sp⟦amac⟧nn</ets> chip + <ets>n⟦ymac⟧r</ets> new. See
<er>Spoon</er>, and <er>New</er>.]</ety> <def>Quite new; brand-new;
fire-new.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>span-new</xex> archbishop's chair.⟦rdquo⟧
